{"tid":1550354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每當有手吹落單被捉，就要大叫: 救人呀","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:39:35.000Z","uid":140309,"like":160,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"85a41449dacc0fc3a5bcd043b93201461859edc5","tid":1550354,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"撕聲裂肺咁大叫: <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！</span></span>，唔好再嗌放人喇<br />\n之後衝埋去救人，用全身力量<span style=\"color: red;\">奮身撞擊</span>係最有效嘅攻擊法方，而且棍、椒、盾係阻你唔到，<span style=\"color: red;\">食一下椒同棍就救到手足，值番哂啦</span><br />\n用<span style=\"color: red;\">速度</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">人數</span>救人，趁對方未有增援就要救人<br />\n<br />\n你唔單止救咗佢令佢唔洗畀人打到重傷，<span style=\"color: red;\">仲救埋佢下半生嘅前途</span><br />\n<br />\n唔洗開遮對峙，唔洗遮掩，<span style=\"color: red;\">刻不容緩，立即行動！ </span> 你就當最多食佢一棍啦<br />\n<br />\n重拾6月9當晚救人嘅勇氣大叫: <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救人呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f3c0b5512b40edd02228409efcf5a2422f38ed5","tid":1550354,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:41:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79b66920db94bfa5db6d1fc6a2c35c4a4f068b18","tid":1550354,"uid":140309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"撕聲裂肺咁大叫:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救人呀&nbsp;！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbaf73b44c0945413e59cc264b75ba90b6095f1f","tid":1550354,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"[警世][最終文宣] 喚醒對中共既不信任 聯合世界圍堵#Chinazi<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60191e039b78a5f0639d36a222f6b046de771b38","tid":1550354,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:17.000Z","msg":"[警世][最終文宣] 喚醒對中共既不信任 聯合世界圍堵#Chinazi<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d381c285d016c613810a3f195b39ee9b5744bd5a","tid":1550354,"uid":140309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"撕聲裂肺咁大嗌:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救人呀！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c02524bb3fb2f7dab0de7fc427b6da2c6abe61e1","tid":1550354,"uid":201604,"